channel.title: Price check
channel.description:
I've really grown tired of RS so I'm looking to sell most of my accounts. Not doing so on these forums as it's not allowed, but I'd like a basic estimate of what I would be able to get for these accounts. Currency either in EUR, USD or RSGP (which I can easily sell off at a later time).
Main since RSC: 123+12 =135 COMBAT About 100 ovls, 4k extreme attack and 4k extreme strength potions in bank in addition to fire cape, torso, full elite void, korasi blah blah, 283QP etc. I've been trying to sell it for over a week for anything between 200-300M / 120-150$ but no luck. Oh the acc also has a rapier, can kill frost drags as you can see, 5 skills at 99, charms to 87 summoning (83 atm) and a crapton of other junk in bank.
[IMG]http://i55.tinypic.com/2e0ogsk.png[/img]
Random 1 def "pure": 52 COMBAT, virtually no wealth, apart from visible stats most are 1 (12 summoning). [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/b66f6o.png[/img]
COMBAT 68: no wealth, full sara book, [IMG]http://i54.tinypic.com/2hdv9j9.png[/img]
COMBAT 92: 100k wealth [IMG]http://i56.tinypic.com/106fvid.png[/img]
I have tons more but cbf to upload pics.
Also got these names, most lvl 3, made in 2008, if they're worth anything.
1) Short Cream 2) Expory 3) I P V (level 21 I think or something) 4) Beat A Wife 5) Antarts 6) Rifk W T F 7) Chammal 8) Saevs 9) Kaits Reborn 10) Anraco 11) Recropped 12) Stork Style (LOL) 13) Depensive
